data.title: Actors John Wayne and Esperanza Baur applying for marriage license in Los Angeles, Calif., 1946
data.meta_description: LICENSE: Actor John Wayne and Esperanza Baur, Mexican film actress, as they applied for marriage license yesterday. They will be married this afternoon.
